LMAO at all the people who want to download torrents but can't figure out a archives.

1. select all zip file (unl-tt01.....unl-tt32)
2. right click (im using 7zip)
3. click extract to "*"
4. now u have unl-ttbs.rar and the archives file (unl-ttbr00.....unl-ttbr30)
5. extract the unl-ttbs
6. instal the game
